8) "A tyrant is wandering around everywhere. Just get divorced."

9) "I marry my ex-wife for five reasons: trust, care, intoxicate, love and sexual denial."

10) "My husband's 'coldy' trousers make the top of my 'lunch' list. Let's have a divorce."

11) "Nobody owns the other. If people are compatible with each other, they should not divorce."
